name: GroupActivityActivationResult
desc: The result of preparing to start a custom activity.

items.name: case activationPreferred
items.desc: A result that indicates the user wants to share the activity with the group.

items.name: case activationDisabled
items.desc: A result that indicates the user disabled the automatic sharing of activities, or prefers to perform the activity locally.

items.name: case cancelled
items.desc: A result that indicates the user canceled the activation request.
